SUMMARY:The Paper Menagerie
DESCRIPTION:Amy McElwain is a collage mixed media artist living in Solano County. She has had creative outlets all of her life and turning the animals who share our planet into colorful\, whimsical renderings is her current passion. Come visit her show\, The Paper Menagerie\, which can be viewed at The Paint Chip\, 217 F Street\, Davis\, CA for the month of March. Reception Friday\, March 13\, 6-8:30pm. You can see more of her work at artbyamymac.com\, on Instagram at artbyamymac\, and on Facebook at Art by Amy Mac.
